primaryTopic.definition: The College of Business, Law and Governance was formed in 2014 to provide new opportunities and collaborations for both education and research. There is a focus on ethics, sustainability and governance, as well as an understanding of complex business systems. The college delivers a range of courses in Cairns, Singapore, Townsville and Brisbane.
